txt.en: Sworn to dark elemental forces, the Agmarim Sorceress uses her granted power to cripple the enemy, rend their flesh, and reinforce her allies.

Angmarim names come from the ancient speech of the TÃ©uta, the Hill-folk of Eriador, a musical tongue roughened by the influence of Black Speech. Common initial elements include Bren-, Cam-, Fin-, Mer-, Sor-, and Tar-.\n\nSome common final elements are -ara, -dakh, -kha, -lig, -nan, -ona, and -ven.
